Name: focus

Synonyms: focusing, focussing, focused, focussed, focusses, focus,
keyboard focus

Type: glossary

Description:
The active status of a window or <control>, in which the window or
<control> can receive input from the keyboard. The <control> that
currently has the focus receives any <character|characters> the user
types. 

References: character (glossary), control (glossary)

Tags: ui

